      <title>金价飙升促使印度人回收婚礼珠宝</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/surging-gold-prompts-indians-to-recycle-jewelry-for-weddings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着印度这个仅次于中国的最大贵金属消费国在婚礼季节需求增加，金价飙升促使一些印度人用金饰换新首饰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/surging-gold-prompts-indians-to-recycle-jewelry-for-weddings</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 09:50:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典央行行长表示犯罪可能造成长期经济打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/riksbank-governor-says-crime-could-cause-long-term-economic-hit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典央行行长埃里克·塞丁（Erik Thedeen）表示，瑞典枪支犯罪盛行可能对这个北欧国家的繁荣构成长期威胁，他与商界领袖一样对近年来震撼该国的帮派暴力表示担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/riksbank-governor-says-crime-could-cause-long-term-economic-hit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 09:47:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
